- User Events: [UserEventsTest.php](mdc:.simulation/15_laravel_events/tests/Feature/Events/UserEventsTest.php)
- Event Listeners: [UserEventListenersTest.php](mdc:.simulation/15_laravel_events/tests/Feature/Listeners/UserEventListenersTest.php)

## Event Types
1. User Registration
   - Event: UserRegistered
   - Broadcasting: PrivateChannel('user.{id}')
   - Queue: Yes
   - Data: User model

2. User Authentication
   - Events: UserLoggedIn, UserLoggedOut
   - Broadcasting: PresenceChannel('users.online')
   - Queue: Yes
   - Data: User model, session duration

3. User Profile
   - Event: UserProfileUpdated
   - Broadcasting: PrivateChannel('user.{id}')
   - Queue: Yes
   - Data: User model, profile changes

4. User Security
   - Event: UserPasswordChanged
   - Broadcasting: PrivateChannel('user.{id}')
   - Queue: Yes
   - Data: User model, IP address

